{"tid":347311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"viu 俾人hack 左？","createTime":"2017-08-04T17:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T17:09:45.000Z","uid":2536,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"458b9a836fa301da73f8f0b5c2f2ad92bc1bf5f9","tid":347311,"uid":2536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/010257_69617daa6e022cd2e82cb1b4689c7c86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F010257_69617daa6e022cd2e82cb1b4689c7c86.jpg&h=24d3e39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知講緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6029f40641e7d57171232ce19b195122f9c73481","tid":347311,"uid":2707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg